<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-full">
{% render "head", title_suffix: "DSPy.rb - Build Reliable LLM Applications in Ruby" %}
<body class="h-full">
  <div class="bg-white">
    {% render "header" %}

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="relative isolate px-6 pt-14 lg:px-8">
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 -top-40 -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden blur-3xl sm:-top-80" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="relative left-[calc(50%-11rem)] aspect-[1155/678] w-[36.125rem] -translate-x-1/2 rotate-[30deg] bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#ff80b5] to-[#9089fc] opacity-30 sm:left-[calc(50%-30rem)] sm:w-[72.1875rem]" style="clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)"></div>
      </div>
      
      {{ content }}
      
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-[calc(100%-13rem)] -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden blur-3xl sm:top-[calc(100%-30rem)]" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="relative left-[calc(50%+3rem)] aspect-[1155/678] w-[36.125rem] -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#ff80b5] to-[#9089fc] opacity-30 sm:left-[calc(50%+36rem)] sm:w-[72.1875rem]" style="clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-dspy-ruby">Build with confidence</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Everything you need to build reliable LLM applications</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600"><a href="https://github.com/vicentereig/dspy.rb">DSPy.rb</a> brings software engineering best practices to LLM development. Type-safe interfaces, composable modules, and systematic testing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-dspy-ruby">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 16.5V9.75m0 0l3 3m-3-3l-3 3M6.75 19.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.41-8.775 5.25 5.25 0 0110.233-2.33 3 3 0 013.758 3.848A3.752 3.752 0 0118 19.5H6.75z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              Type-Safe Interfaces
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Define your LLM interfaces using familiar Ruby syntax with Sorbet types. No more string manipulation or JSON schema headaches.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-dspy-ruby">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              Composable Modules
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Build complex LLM applications from simple, tested modules. Chain reasoning steps, handle errors gracefully, and create reusable components.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-dspy-ruby">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 16.875h3.375m0 0h3.375m-3.375 0V13.5m0 3.375v3.375M6 10.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V6a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 10.5zm0 9.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0010.5 18v-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 006 20.25zm9.75-9.75H18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V6A2.25 2.25 0 0018 3.75h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0013.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              Systematic Testing
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Test your LLM applications like any other code. Our comprehensive test suite with 226+ specs proves everything works as expected.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-dspy-ruby">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.864 4.243A7.5 7.5 0 0119.5 10.5c0 2.92-.556 5.709-1.568 8.268M5.742 6.364A7.465 7.465 0 004.5 10.5a7.464 7.464 0 01-1.15 3.993m1.989 3.559A11.209 11.209 0 008.25 10.5a3.75 3.75 0 117.5 0c0 .527-.021 1.049-.064 1.565M12 10.5a14.94 14.94 0 01-3.6 9.75m6.633-4.596a18.666 18.666 0 01-2.485 5.33" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              Ruby Ecosystem
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Built on Ruby's mature ecosystem. Integrate with Rails, Sidekiq, and other tools you already know and trust.</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-700 to-red-800">
    <div class="px-6 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Ready to build reliable LLM applications?</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-red-100">Stop fighting with prompt engineering. Start building LLM applications that actually work in production.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
          <a href="{{ '/getting-started/' | relative_url }}" class="rounded-md bg-white px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-dspy-ruby shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white">Get started</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/vicentereig/dspy.rb" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-red-100">View on GitHub <span aria-hidden="true">â†’</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% render "footer" %}
</body>
</html>